Titolo: Mercenary (video game)

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Mercenary is a 3D action-adventure game written for the Atari 8-bit family and published by Novagen Software in 1985. It was converted to the Commodore 64, ZX Spectrum, Amstrad CPC, Atari ST, Amiga and Commodore 16/116/Plus/4 platforms. The game uses vector graphics renderings of vast, sparse environments and has open-ended gameplay. It was also released as Mercenary: Escape from Targ and Mercenary: A Flight Simulator Adventure. 
Mercenary was favourably reviewed and followed by two sequels: Damocles and Mercenary III: The Dion Crisis.